    question: 'Omnisend or Attentive for cart recovery?',
    answer: 'Choose Omnisend when SMB Shopify stores wanting multichannel automation without enterprise complexity. Choose Attentive when Larger DTC brands with high SMS volume. Sequenzy still leads as lifecycle layer if neither owns strategy.',
